# File Structure

## Layout

```
.
├── frontend/          # React 19 dashboard (Bun)
│   └── src/
│       ├── index.ts       # Bun server (SPA + /api proxy)
│       ├── frontend.tsx   # React entry
│       ├── App.tsx
│       ├── index.css      # Global styles
│       ├── types.ts       # Shared types
│       └── components/    # React components
├── producer/          # Hono REST API + Kafka publisher
│   └── src/
│       ├── index.ts       # App bootstrap
│       ├── db.ts          # MongoDB client
│       ├── kafka.ts       # Kafka producer
│       └── routes/        # Route modules (e.g. tasks.ts)
├── consumer/          # Kafka consumer → MongoDB
│   └── src/index.ts
├── k8s/               # Kubernetes manifests
└── docker-compose.yml
```

## Conventions

- **Routes**: One file per resource under `producer/src/routes/`. Export as `taskRoutes`, `xyzRoutes`.
- **Components**: PascalCase in `frontend/src/components/`. One component per file; export named.
- **Types**: Shared types in `frontend/src/types.ts`. Backend types inline or in route/module.
- **Config**: Environment variables with sensible defaults. No `.env` committed.
- **K8s**: One manifest per service. Namespace `data-ingest`. Labels `app: <service>`.
